Italian CPI , BoP heading in right direction - Fazio . Bank of Italy governor Antonio Fazio said Italy ' s exchange rates , inflation and balance of payments were heading in the right direction . " The markets are performing quite well , exchange rates , balance of payments and inflation seem to be going in the right direction , " he told reporters after a meeting of G10 central bank governors . " There ' s some sign of economic recovery in Europe , " he added . 
